no, it's sejuani. the guy "climbing" is Ambition, Jungler for SSG the team that won worlds last year.
he has 3 weapons throughout the music video
Kha'ziks claws (facing Perkz as Yasuo)
Sejuanis chain mace thing (facing Uzi as Vayne)
and finally Jarvan IVs spear (facing Faker as Ryze), Jarvan IV being the champion he was on for the match that won his team worlds. and the champion he picked for his team skin.
all 3 are champions he played throughout worlds.

I keep thinking about this and laughing at the most random of moments. 
10/10
